Author: Jérôme Piquot <jpiquot@itaneo.com>
Date:   Mon May 18 22:37:13 2026 +0200

    feat: Implement organization ACL management
    
    - Added OrganizationAclEntryKey record to represent unique ACL entries.
    - Introduced OrganizationAclOperation and OrganizationAclOperationIntent for managing ACL operations.
    - Created OrganizationAclPrincipalGranted and OrganizationAclPrincipalRevoked records for event representation.
    - Defined OrganizationAclResult and OrganizationAclResultCode for handling command results.
    - Implemented OrganizationAclTenantGate for processing ACL commands with tenant authorization.
    - Developed OrganizationAggregate to handle ACL operations and maintain state.
    - Established OrganizationState to track grants and idempotency fingerprints.
    - Created OrganizationStreamName for generating stream names based on tenant and organization.
    - Added commands for granting and revoking ACL principals.
    - Implemented unit tests for ACL command validation, effective permissions, idempotency, and metadata leakage.
    - Developed a recording repository for testing purposes to track repository interactions.

